CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 9, 1958, pg. A13, reads: "Dental Dignitaries - W. F. Swanson, dean of the university's School of Dentistry, second from left, chats with, left, Dr. Russell A. Dixon, dean of Howard University's College of Dentistry; right, Dr. Harold D. West, president, Meharry Medical College, Nashville, and Dr. Ulysses W. Williams, local convention chairman. - All Photos by Teenie Harris."
TitMainTitle: Attendees of 45th Annual Session National Dental Association, W. F. Swanson, Dr. Russell A. Dixon, Dr. Harold D. West, and Dr. Ulysses W. Williams at Penn - Sheraton Hotel
